house.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=ee364cb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7577bbf6f032215e6f6e29b6dc5f49046cea3ea3","tid":2209354,"uid":346260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"87fa34d1c5aa5547855993eef0f55967cef67287","tid":2209354,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"人地家事感情事 個老公都未出聲 幾時輪到你<br />\n皇帝唔急太監急"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"人地講咩唔講咩關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"727a365d625647083292b394b9db8fefcc3c3c3b","tid":2209354,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7577bbf6f032215e6f6e29b6dc5f49046cea3ea3","tid":2209354,"uid":346260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"87fa34d1c5aa5547855993eef0f55967cef67287","tid":2209354,"uid":73565,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"人地家事感情事 個老公都未出聲 幾時輪到你<br />\n皇帝唔急太監急"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"人地講咩唔講咩關你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T03:28:36.000Z","msg":"佢上黎求助 唔俾得意見？"},{"pid":"fac225f3ed96bf732b2521ce564d4d29e615d7f1","tid":2209354,"uid":346260,"like":0,